0	<text font="9" height="13" left="103" textpieces="0" top="1032" width="340">of the exported texts may not reï¬‚ect the human reading</text>
 
0	<text font="9" height="13" left="103" textpieces="0" top="1050" width="340">ordering. The text sequence error is a common problem</text>
 
