0	<text font="9" height="13" left="475" textpieces="0" top="1067" width="340">text extraction tools usually export a part of the table con-</text>
 
0	<text font="7" height="11" left="447" textpieces="0" top="1112" width="24">1007</text>
 
0	<text font="8" height="8" left="107" textpieces="0" top="1175" width="555">Authorized licensed use limited to: Penn State University. Downloaded on February 9, 2010 at 16:37 from IEEE Xplore.  Restrictions apply. </text>
 
