0	<text font="4" height="14" left="82" textpieces="0" top="1048" width="360">by combining the table caption information. We deï¬ne a</text>
 
0	<text font="4" height="14" left="82" textpieces="0" top="1066" width="360">keyword list, which lists all the possible starting keywords</text>
 
