0	<text font="4" height="14" left="476" textpieces="1" top="180" width="358">formance improvement on bothP and R because all the</text>
 
0	<text font="4" height="14" left="476" textpieces="0" top="198" width="358">lines belong to the table boundary come together without</text>
 
