0	<text font="4" height="14" left="476" textpieces="0" top="235" width="358">quence errors, the performance is much worse without our</text>
 
0	<text font="4" height="14" left="476" textpieces="1" top="253" width="358">algorithms: with the same test PDFs, theR is only 63.5%</text>
 
